dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Eric Ramirez. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Debra. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for security verification?
Sure, my policy number is five six eight seven two one and my date of birth is zero four slash twelve slash nineteen eighty.
Thank you, Debra. I also need your current mailing address and contact number. Could you please provide me with that information?
Of course. My mailing address is two four five Cedar Street, Greenfield, and my contact number is five five five - two five five - seven eight nine zero.
Thank you for providing the information, Debra. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Eric.
You're welcome, Debra. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
